Best Seller Notification


                      Free e-mail announcement of new products
          A free e-mail service notifying you of our best selling products

   Tell Me Why
   NTIS receives a number of important publications, CD-ROM's,
   audiovisuals, and other products throughout the year. We want to alert
   you when these important items are first received by NTIS.

   Tell Me More
   This service offers free e-mail notification that conveniently brings
   to your attention, news and updates about essential NTIS products and
   services that can impact your information needs:
     * Be the first to know when those annual "best sellers" are due to be
       released by the publisher
     * Read about special reports that warrant a "product announcement"
     * Receive advance notice of special or prepublication pricing on
       selected documents
     * Obtain information about new products and services
     * And, of course, receive updates on NTIS enhanced customer service

   Tell Me How    top of page pointer
   It's easy to subscribe to NTIS E-Update, and it's free. All you need is
   an e-mail address. We do the rest. To subscribe, enter your e-mail
   address below and click the "Subscribe" button.

   If you have any problems contact: webmaster@ntis.gov

